verbose_text: As shown in XREF_FIG, after treatment with various concentrations of N-Ac-PGP for 1 day, increases in the secretion of IL-1beta, IL-6, IL-17, CCL2 and TNF-alpha by NP cells were observed regardless of the concentration of N-Ac-PGP.
evidence: increases in the secretion of IL-1beta, IL-6, IL-17, CCL2 and TNF-alpha by NP
